.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-LOCAL-RESERVE-MEDIAN" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-local-reserve-median \- FEAT-2642 channel-local-reserve-median
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-local-reserve-median
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the median local_reserve_msat across all peer channels for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2642).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
